  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=606 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/1ee42adb8a7341ca672eb161f746d27b.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Bullet hell</strong> meets <strong>auto-shooter</strong> in this <strong>roguelike color-matcher</strong> where RGB itself is your weapon! Wield the might of the light spectrum as you alternate between different hues in order to exploit your foes' weaknesses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/0b3fa655b7c8e6a9b4014038d9220af1.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In a plane of existence beyond our comprehension, the <strong>Maiden of Light</strong> controls, creates, and regulates the entire visible spectrum as we know it. The diabolical forces of entropy have captured the Maiden, intent on draining her power and plunging the world into darkness. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.poster.avif?t=1728059993\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.webm?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2161280/extras/a1d6eefd2a94e0f4c2c6cea1d2757b65.mp4?t=1728059993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a mote of light blessed by the will of the Maiden, you must rise up against insurmountable odds. <strong>Multiple challenging bosses stand in your way and only you can save her!</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REFLEXES & WIT-</h2> the <strong>color matching</strong> system adds a layer of <strong>complexity</strong> to the traditional shooter format<br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLESSINGS OF A GODDESS- </h2><strong>upgrades</strong> which can be combined for a variety of <strong>unique playstyles</strong><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >JAMMIN' TUNES-</h2> a <strong>curated soundtrack</strong> featuring a variety of exciting <strong>D&B, techno, and electronica</strong> tracks</li></ul>",
